ime":"2018-02-20T05:00:53.000Z","msg":"明顯check哂諗好哂先拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:01:22.000Z","msg":"可能識睇某啲字，<br />\n但又唔知咩食物呢。<br />\n<br />\n凱薩沙津，可能識睇沙津，但唔知咩係凱薩呢。<br />\n尖椒牛雙蓮，識睇牛，但唔知乜鬼係牛雙蓮呢。"},{"pid":"5df54a685cefb1c84647615adb81968e95b795a3","tid":564561,"uid":55937,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"TVB藝人 同 高貴&hellip;&hellip;大纜都扯唔埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a942dc9d2770a088c2b92da7fbafc5a20dc59c","tid":564561,"uid":131158,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:08:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%99%B3%E6%99%BA%E7%87%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%2599%25BA%25E7%2587%258A&d=0%2FjgaY9T%2BBAXZAwhpOOyor%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=b61eff67\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%99%B3%E6%99%BA%E7%87%8A</a><br />\n<br />\n教育程度\t倫敦大學亞非學院古典及現代中國文學學士<br />\n<br />\n唔識中文???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>樓上話佢地要google 翻譯 <br />\n識睇仲要翻譯?</blockquote><a href=\"http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/13242\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2F13242&d=0%2FjgaY9T%2BBAXZAwhpOOyor%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=af3b102a\" target=\"_blank\">http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/13242</a><br />\n<br />\n升讀大學時，他為了將來方便搵工，揀選修讀經濟和語文，十八九歲才正式認真去學中文。「睇同寫，之前除咗我個名之外，只係識『你』、『我』、『日』、『月』好簡單嘅單字，算係唔識o架。後來我讀大學時，有年要去北京留學，咪狂寫囉，好似寫copybook咁，寫滿一張A4紙，寫到我記得為止囉！真係一個好艱苦嘅過程呀！最衰狂寫完，之後都未必記得啲筆畫係點寫喎，又冇得拼音拼出嚟，好難！『你』、『我』、『吃』、『飯』，嘩！寫到人都癲呀！所以我好唔明，香港啲細路仔，點學中文o架？狂寫copybook，好悶o架喎！」<br />\n<br />\n日子有功，幾年努力學習中文，換來的，是今天睇劇本不用寫譯音咁煩。「真係甚少！可能間中有啲字會唔識或唔明個意思囉。」</blockquote>即係基本上都識啦<br />\nMenu啲中文字應該唔會難得去邊掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁如果佢識睇又點解要拎電話google translate呢？唔係為左連戲比巴打睇掛？讀過書都明你考試操得最fit果陣同一年後問返你啲terms，都真係未必記得，如果佢識講中文但特登同你講英文果啲就真係串喇"},{"pid":"d1df1ba6dae130a23ab2d70e03feaf0f16fe152e","tid":564561,"uid":52020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5df54a685cefb1c84647615adb81968e95b795a3","tid":564561,"uid":55937,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"TVB藝人 同 高貴&hellip;&hellip;大纜都扯唔埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:17:36.000Z","msg":"DO姐"},{"pid":"3d2fc2762b3a7606502a1090532ab2f55c29cd53","tid":564561,"uid":128596,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:29:01.000Z","msg":"李壁琪咁既八婆樣都叫高貴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfbcaf25bd216c56b8a07b5e2dedf9be28aa6e4","tid":564561,"uid":130907,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:03:00.000Z","msg":"莊思敏講野好似含住舊野咁，好生硬，成個格好八婆，做呢類角色最岩，不過一睇到佢就想熄電視。李壁琦做明珠台好好，講英文好正，但一做戲就感覺好老土，可能角色既問題。<br />\n<br />\n貴氣既可能是前藝人楊洛婷？聽講做婚禮司儀，一開口講英文，成場靜曬。陳貝兒都ok。"},{"pid":"a1e5a9b761dad031b53c59408ba37c079f80c2d1","tid":564561,"uid":12755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:07:17.000Z","msg":"唔出圖真係唔知你講邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ea4f52d8fe1fbfdef9160a95bf25b35a0b952c","tid":564561,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:14:09.000Z","msg":"宋熙年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1818bf605c4e7ce4583b8698cbac69591f167d37","tid":564561,"uid":19218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1be5e0b73380d3c5f0dd6c23eb98c614882940df","tid":564561,"uid":81569,"like":94,"dislike":32